Finds the Chebyshev expansion coefficients of a given polynomial\
\>", "TechNoteTableText",ExpressionUUID->
     "4f89df40-e60d-4fe4-b5bc-e5a0e67b7aa8"]},
   {
    TemplateBox[{
      Cell[
       TextData["ChebyshevApproximation"]], 
      "paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/ref/ChebyshevApproximation", 
      "QuantumMob Package Symbol"},
     "PackageLink",
     BaseStyle->{"DefinitionBox", CellFrame -> 0}], Cell["\<\
Finds the Chebyshev expansion coefficients of a polynomial approximating a \
given function\
\>", "TechNoteTableText",ExpressionUUID->
     "67246d86-080a-4375-8dc1-cd9e9eacfb96"]}
  }]], "DefinitionBox",
 CellID->44031775,ExpressionUUID->"561dbb34-7ce0-45f3-8aad-893837da6d21"],

Cell["Q3 functions related to quantum signal processing.", "TechNoteCaption",
 CellID->1307667857,ExpressionUUID->"0525aba8-6473-41bf-90b5-2511fb90c872"],

Cell["The examples here require Q3:", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->626029201,ExpressionUUID->"b0146106-1fc6-46fa-858a-632fb7e7ff8f"],

